ZEsarUX: ZEsarUX (retro machines emulator)
ZEsarUX:
ZEsarUX: ZEsarUX is a ZX Machines Emulator for Unix, including all the
ZEsarUX: Sinclair computers: MK14, ZX80, ZX81, ZX Spectrum, QL, Z88 and
ZEsarUX: also:  Timex TS 2068, Sam Coupe, Pentagon, Chloe 140 SE, 280 SE,
ZEsarUX: Chrome, Prism, ZX-Uno, ZX-Evolution TS-Conf,
ZEsarUX: TBBlue/ZX Spectrum Next, Jupiter Ace and Amstrad CPC 464
ZEsarUX:
ZEsarUX: ZEsarUX also includes third-party roms, media, programs and
ZEsarUX: games NOT covered by the GNU GPL license.
ZEsarUX: Homepage at https://github.com/chernandezba/zesarux
